g/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<blockquote>Unexpected當年有份老屈葉希臨仲周街貼人街貼，炒車後拍拍籮柚走左去<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/10/121845_28c827a15beb3f2fd56f3ca87c8ee2a9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F10%2F121845_28c827a15beb3f2fd56f3ca87c8ee2a9.jpg&h=3c224531&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/10/121947_b974e3bed99b06c62887ea1f82bb725a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F10%2F121947_b974e3bed99b06c62887ea1f82bb725a.jpg&h=63735190&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n比人踢爆佢啲暴行之後竟然否認仲話人改佢圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/10/121901_0c0fda722b625ff30b2e5c3f7913b3ba.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F10%2F121901_0c0fda722b625ff30b2e5c3f7913b3ba.jpg&h=077d6638&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n點知唔夠一陣自打嘴巴，柒左諗住打兩句哈哈輕輕帶過<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/10/121932_3c9314896c5944a6dda79f65eac0a47e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F10%2F121932_3c9314896c5944a6dda79f65eac0a47e.jpg&h=ca09883e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「oh我炒左車呀哈哈，不過條女身敗名裂關我撚事」<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母CC台啲鍵國撚仲係賤過地底泥，害到條女雞毛鴨血但係歉都冇道過，回應個陣仲鬼咁輕佻打幾個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> icon<br />\n<br />\n正一垃圾</blockquote>"},{"pid":"384bdb302d0b7857c4211275e65ccbbd633570e4","tid":534910,"uid":151916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"748e78bbe2c336bb60659288634d46fe807967be","tid":534910,"uid":51978,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T10:06:22.000Z","msg":"我們的互聯網，在助人尋美食的openrice，卻沒有教人搵二手飯的指南。事實上，香港雖然餐廳處處，但不是哪裡也有合適的二手飯，所以要做流浪者，就必須要對鄰近食肆有充掌握。<br />\n<br />\n餐廳1：麥當勞<br />\n<br />\n常見二手美食：薯條、薯餅、可樂、熱香餅、熱香餅專用蜜糖<br />\n<br />\n二手解讀：每位食客離開後，餐盤上幾乎例必留下前三款食物，如閣下是嗜炸物，保證能大快朵頣。熱香餅因有三塊之多，部分女食客可能會食剩一塊半塊，好運者甚至可發現少量豬柳漢堡！另要留意熱香餅用蜜糖，常有餅剩。踏入秋季唇乾舌燥，可充當真蜜糖沖水飲作滋潤喉嚨之用。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n餐廳2：連鎖快餐廳(美心大家樂大快活均可)<br />\n<br />\n常見二手美食：咖哩牛腩飯、栗米肉粒飯(其化頹飯均合)大量白米飯、奶茶、伴碟菜<br />\n<br />\n二手解讀：咖哩牛飯可算是肉眼觀察中常見的二手飯，皆因薯仔太濟，牛腩太有咬口，雖然不少快餐店﹙如大快活﹚，其咖哩牛腩飯味道不錯，但七成以上人仍會食唔晒。至於被視為頹飯的栗米肉粒，往往是不少人揀無可揀之選，進食意慾不高，自然吃剩機會也大。另伴碟菜更是二手飯食客必食之選---伴碟菜由於只為點綴或「叫做有條菜」，通常白烚了事，因味同嚼蠟，所以食客通常棄之一旁。其實食菜有益，二手食客實不容錯過。<br />\n<br />\n建議在進店前，先看水牌，如見有咖哩牛腩和栗米肉粒，能飽餐一頓二手飯的機會勁大。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T13:41:23.000Z","msg":"香港地真係唔會餓死 只會做死"},{"pid":"8308b662328966c1e2f14f9aec37c561c1c2b94e","tid":534910,"uid":138946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T13:45:43.000Z","msg":"叫牙業比你採陽補補佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4666ab577120bf035657abdf63e545ffe917c5c7","tid":534910,"uid":36964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6009af2149a0f1ae6fed5b08383b18dba99017a7","tid":534910,"uid":60959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e998fbebfc1adfa26a6f1dede26ea43b547e5e6","tid":534910,"uid":36964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T12:47:10.000Z","msg":"死返波台開垃圾post啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T13:30:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<blockquote>Unexpected當年有份老屈葉希臨仲周街貼人街貼，炒車後拍拍籮柚走左去<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/10/121845_28c827a15beb3f2fd56f3ca87c8ee2a9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F10%2F121845_28c827a15beb3f2fd56f3ca87c8ee2a9.jpg&h=3c224531&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/10/121947_b974e3bed99b06c62887ea1f82bb725a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"htt